data.description: Remodeled and ready to move into this beautiful Quad Level home. Located in the very desirable Riivendell Subdivision on a heavily wooded 1.34-acre corner lot for privacy. Step right into the large foyer with marble tile. This home features large rooms with loads of upgrades throughout, 3 - 4 bedrooms with ceiling fans, completely remodeled 3 full bathrooms each with porcelain and glass tile work, beautiful touch to each vanity brings everything together. Eat in Kitchen with all Stainless-Steel Kitchen Aid Appliances, Granite Counters, Glass back splash, White Cabinets, Skylight in Kitchen, All new lighting throughout, large laundry room with Samsung Washer and Dryer, Remote start to Family Room Fireplace, Large bedrooms with private Master Bath and loads of Closet space, New Front Door and Patio Door, Sunken Living Room with Coffered Ceilings, Formal Dining Room, Finished basement that can be either the 4th bedroom or a great area rec room to get away to. Tons of storage space in the basement. The asphalt driveway has just been weatherized. There is so many great things about this home you won't be disappointed. Listing agency does not hold earnest money.
